description: Lists completed imports within the past 90 days.

nested_items.name: ImportArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Number (ARN) corresponding to the import request.

nested_items.name: ImportStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the import operation.

nested_items.name: TableArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Number (ARN) of the table being imported into.

nested_items.name: S3BucketSource
nested_items.description: The path and S3 bucket of the source file that is being imported. This includes the S3Bucket (required), S3KeyPrefix (optional) and S3BucketOwner (optional if the bucket is owned by the requester).

nested_items.name: S3BucketOwner
nested_items.description: The account number of the S3 bucket that is being imported from. If the bucket is owned by the requester this is optional.

nested_items.name: S3Bucket
nested_items.description: The S3 bucket that is being imported from.

nested_items.name: S3KeyPrefix
nested_items.description: The key prefix shared by all S3 Objects that are being imported.

nested_items.name: CloudWatchLogGroupArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Number (ARN) of the Cloudwatch Log Group associated with this import task.

nested_items.name: InputFormat
nested_items.description: The format of the source data. Valid values are CSV, DYNAMODB_JSON or ION.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The time at which this import task began.

nested_items.name: EndTime
nested_items.description: The time at which this import task ended. (Does this include the successful complete creation of the table it was imported to?)

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If this value is returned, there are additional results to be displayed. To retrieve them, call ListImports again, with NextToken set to this value.
